---
// WhyChooseUs.astro
const { region, city } = Astro.props;
const location = city || region;
---

<section class="bg-white py-20">
 <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
   <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Why Choose HD IPTV in {location}?</h2>

   <div class="grid gap-12">
     <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
       <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Affordable Entertainment Options</h3>
       <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Break free from expensive cable contracts and embrace the future of television entertainment in {location}. Our UK IPTV subscription services deliver outstanding value, offering comprehensive entertainment packages at competitive prices. Traditional satellite and cable services often require long-term commitments and costly equipment installations, while our IPTV solution provides immediate access to premium content without hidden charges.</p>
       <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We understand every household has unique entertainment needs, which is why we offer flexible subscription in {location} options:</p>
       <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 list-disc pl-6">
         <li>Quarterly subscriptions providing enhanced value</li>
         <li>Annual packages offering maximum savings</li>
         <li>Special bundle deals for multi-room setups</li>
       </ul>
     </div>

     <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
       <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Extensive Channel Selection in {location}</h3>
       <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Experience television without boundaries through our vast IPTV channel selection. Our service brings together an impressive array of content:</p>
       <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 list-disc pl-6">
         <li>Over 15,000 live channels from across the globe</li>
         <li>Complete UK entertainment package including BBC, ITV, and Channel 4</li>
         <li>Premium sports coverage featuring Premier League, Champions League, and Formula 1</li>
         <li>International news networks delivering round-the-clock coverage</li>
         <li>Dedicated children's channels ensuring family-friendly entertainment</li>
         <li>Speciality channels covering documentaries, lifestyle, and cultural content</li>
       </ul>
     </div>

     <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 border-l-4 border-blue-600">
       <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">High-Quality Streaming Experience</h3>
       <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Immerse yourself in superior viewing quality with our advanced streaming infrastructure:</p>
       <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 list-disc pl-6">
         <li>Full HD 1080p streaming as standard</li>
         <li>4K Ultra HD content availability for compatible devices</li>
         <li>Optimized servers ensuring minimal buffering</li>
         <li>Smart bandwidth management for consistent performance</li>
         <li>Multiple server locations guaranteeing 99.9% uptime</li>
         <li>Advanced encoding for crystal-clear picture quality</li>
       </ul>
     </div>
   </div>
 </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
