         <li>Catch-up TV functionality for missed programs</li>
         <li>Regular content updates ensuring fresh entertainment</li>
         <li>Exclusive documentaries and special features</li>
       </ul>
     </div>

     <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
       <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
         <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-600 mr-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
           <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
         </svg>
         Built-In VPN for Secure Streaming
       </h3>
       <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Your privacy and security matter. Our integrated VPN service provides:</p>
       <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8">
         <li>Military-grade encryption protecting your streaming activity</li>
         <li>Prevention of ISP throttling for smoother playback</li>
         <li>Anonymous viewing experience</li>
         <li>Protection on public Wi-Fi networks</li>
